'''TAO'''是於1993年在[[日本|日本]][[愛知縣|愛知縣]]成立的[[太鼓|太鼓]][[樂團|樂團]]，目前駐在[[九州_(日本)|九州]][[大分縣|大分縣]][[竹田市|竹田市]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=DRUM TAOの概要|url=http://www.drum-tao.com/main/whoweare|publisher=DRUM TAO|accessdate=2014-01-09|archive-date=2014-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109180250/http://www.drum-tao.com/main/whoweare|dead-url=no}}</ref> 他們的表演風格除了表現日本的傳統音樂和舞蹈，同時也結合了[[朝鮮|朝鮮]]、[[毛利人|紐西蘭]]和[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]]的表演特色。<ref>{{cite news|title=Tao: The Martial Art of Drumming bangs its way into Fort Worth|url=http://www.pegasusnews.com/news/2010/feb/03/tao-martial-art-drumming-bangs-its-way-fort-worth/|newspaper=Pegasus News|date=2010-02-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100205181922/http://www.pegasusnews.com/news/2010/feb/03/tao-martial-art-drumming-bangs-its-way-fort-worth/|archivedate=2010-02-05|accessdate=2014-01-09}}</ref><ref name="A">{{cite news|author=Stephen Bevis|title=Sweat and tears for drum troupe|url=http://fddp.theage.com.au/news/arts/sweat-and-tears-for-drum-troupe/2008/07/06/1215282643581.html|publisher=The Age|date=2008-07-07|accessdate=2015-01-07|archive-date=2015-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108010210/http://fddp.theage.com.au/news/arts/sweat-and-tears-for-drum-troupe/2008/07/06/1215282643581.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> TAO的表演作品除了部分是傳統的日本歌曲，大多數都是由樂團成員原創的現代作品。

TAO演奏使用的[[打擊樂器|打擊樂器]]大多時候是6－10個[[太鼓|組太鼓]]，但在一些曲目中會結合[[篠笛|篠笛]]、[[竹木琴|竹木琴]]、[[鑼|鑼]]和[[日本筝|日本筝]]等樂器。<ref>{{cite news|author=John Stanley|title=Japanese taiko drum corps at Mesa Arts Center|url=http://www.azcentral.com/thingstodo/stage/articles/2010/02/17/20100217japanese-taiko-drum-corps0217.html?nclick_check=1|newspaper=The Arizona Republic|date=2010-02-17}}</ref> 他們除了在日本演出，也曾經在英國、德國、澳洲、紐西蘭、美國、加拿大、韓國、台灣、新加坡<ref>{{cite news|author=Ariel Gwee|title=Drum Tao: Where music meets fashion and comedy|url=http://entertainment.xin.msn.com/en/celebrity/buzz/asia/drum-tao-where-music-meets-fashion-and-comedy|newspaper=MSN|date=2013-08-01|access-date=2014-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110121112/http://entertainment.xin.msn.com/en/celebrity/buzz/asia/drum-tao-where-music-meets-fashion-and-comedy|archive-date=2014-01-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 、馬來西亞<ref>{{cite news|author=Natalie White|title=TAO {{!}} The Art of the Drum|url=http://senatus.net/event/tao-art-drum/|newspaper=Senatus.Net|date=2012-08-24|accessdate=2014-01-10|archive-date=2014-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110123049/http://senatus.net/event/tao-art-drum/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 等世界20國及400個城市巡迴公演，<ref>{{cite web|title=世界のDRUM TAO|url=http://www.drum-tao.com/main/whoweare|publisher=DRUM TAO|accessdate=2014-01-09|archive-date=2014-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109180250/http://www.drum-tao.com/main/whoweare|dead-url=no}}</ref>  及參加過2004年的英國[[愛丁堡藝穗節|愛丁堡藝穗節]]街頭匯演。

